OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775578269
OL,3,CPine martens' 'elusive woodland
OL,4,Cantics' captured on camera
OL,6,FWatch: Three pine marten kits
OL,7,Fexploring their forest home. (Credit:
OL,8,FTwo Moors Pine Marten Project)
OL,10,FThe "elusive woodland antics" of pine
OL,11,Fmartens in the South West of England
OL,12,Fhave been captured by trail cameras on
OL,13,FDartmoor and Exmoor.
OL,15,FIt comes as experts say the animals
OL,16,Fare "doing well" since their recent
OL,17,Freintroduction and have begun to
OL,18,Fproduce young.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
