OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775578269
OL,3,CPine martens' 'elusive woodland
OL,4,Cantics' captured on camera
OL,6,FAli North, the project's Exmoor field
OL,7,Fofficer, said: "Pine martens are a
OL,8,Fhighly mobile species and so they have
OL,9,Fkept us very busy trying to keep track
OL,10,Fof them.
OL,12,F"We're excited to moving into the next
OL,13,Fphase of our monitoring using camera
OL,14,Ftraps to catch a glimpse into their
OL,15,Felusive woodland antics.
OL,17,F"We hope many landowners will want to
OL,18,Fget involved in our newly launched
OL,19,Fwoodland citizen science survey to
OL,20,Fhelp us track their distribution over
OL,21,Ftime."
OL,26,@oD@POU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
